#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.normal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.normal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:1 of
msgid "Draw random samples from a normal (Gaussian) distribution."
msgstr "从正态（高斯）分布中抽取随机样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:3 of
msgid ""
"The probability density function of the normal distribution, first "
"derived by De Moivre and 200 years later by both Gauss and Laplace "
"independently [2]_, is often called the bell curve because of its "
"characteristic shape (see the example below)."
msgstr ""
"正态分布的概率密度函数最初由 De Moivre 推导出来，200 年后由 Gauss 和 "
"Laplace 独立重新推导 [2]_，由于其典型的形状常被称为钟形曲线（参见下面的"
"示例）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:8 of
msgid ""
"The normal distributions occurs often in nature.  For example, it "
"describes the commonly occurring distribution of samples influenced by a "
"large number of tiny, random disturbances, each with its own unique "
"distribution [2]_."
msgstr ""
"正态分布在自然界中经常出现。例如，它描述了受大量微小、随机干扰影响的样本"
"的常见分布，每个干扰都有其独特的分布 [2]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:13 of
msgid "Mean (\"centre\") of the distribution."
msgstr "分布的均值（“中心”）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:15 of
msgid "Standard deviation (spread or \"width\") of the distribution."
msgstr "分布的标准差（离散度或“宽度”）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:17 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``loc`` and ``scale`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``mt.broadcast(loc, scale).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则会抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``loc`` 和 ``scale`` 都为标量，则"
"返回单个值。否则，抽取 ``mt.broadcast(loc, scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:22 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:24 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:26 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:29 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized normal distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的正态分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.norm`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:35 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:38 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:39 of
msgid "The probability density for the Gaussian distribution is"
msgstr "高斯分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:41 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{ 2 \\pi \\sigma^2 }}\n"
"e^{ - \\frac{ (x - \\mu)^2 } {2 \\sigma^2} },\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:44 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\mu` is the mean and :math:`\\sigma` the standard "
"deviation. The square of the standard deviation, :math:`\\sigma^2`, is "
"called the variance."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\mu` 是均值，:math:`\\sigma` 是标准差。标准差的平方 :math:`"
"\\sigma^2`，称为方差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:48 of
msgid ""
"The function has its peak at the mean, and its \"spread\" increases with "
"the standard deviation (the function reaches 0.607 times its maximum at "
":math:`x + \\sigma` and :math:`x - \\sigma` [2]_).  This implies that "
"`numpy.random.normal` is more likely to return samples lying close to the"
" mean, rather than those far away."
msgstr ""
"该函数在均值处达到峰值，其“离散度”随标准差增加而增大（函数在 :math:`x +"
" \\sigma` 和 :math:`x - \\sigma` 处达到最大值的 0.607 倍 [2]_）。这意味着"
" `numpy.random.normal` 更可能返回接近均值的样本，而不是远离均值的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:55 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:56 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Normal distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Normal_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:58 of
msgid ""
"P. R. Peebles Jr., \"Central Limit Theorem\" in \"Probability, Random "
"Variables and Random Signal Principles\", 4th ed., 2001, pp. 51, 51, 125."
msgstr ""
"P. R. Peebles Jr., \"Central Limit Theorem\" in \"Probability, Random "
"Variables and Random Signal Principles\", 第 4 版, 2001, 第 51, 51, 125 "
"页。"

