msgid "Verify the mean and the variance:"
msgstr "验证均值和方差："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.normal.normal:79 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

